<section class="wrapper region flow prose" id="CollaborationOptions">
  <div class="box w-fit mx-auto text-center">
    <h2>Collaboration options</h2>
    <p>
      Collaborations can be scoped for your owned channels, a selective Skin
      Schema feature, or a custom content bundle built around your campaign
      goals.
    </p>
  </div>
  <ul class="grid" data-layout="50-50" role="list">
    <li
      class="box flow prose border border-gray-600 drop mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-clip"
    >
      <h3
        class="mt-zero text-step-000 uppercase font-black text-gray-1100 font-mono"
      >
        Option 1
      </h3>
      <h4 class="mt-2xs text-step-2">For Brand Use</h4>
      <p class="text-step-00">
        Receive polished short-form videos, product storytelling, texture
        visuals, or photo sets created for your social channels, launch moments,
        campaigns, and product education. Each piece is planned, shot, and
        edited to feel minimal, airy, and commercially ready. †
      </p>
    </li>
    <li
      class="box flow prose border border-gray-600 drop mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-clip"
    >
      <h3
        class="mt-zero text-step-000 uppercase font-black text-gray-1100 font-mono"
      >
        Option 2
      </h3>
      <h4 class="mt-2xs text-step-2">Shared by Skin Schema</h4>
      <p class="text-step-00">
        For strong brand fits, your product can be introduced through Skin
        Schema's beauty point of view and shared with an audience that values
        refined visuals, thoughtful product context, and genuine skincare and
        makeup recommendations.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="text-center mx-auto text-step-000 text-gray-1000">
    † Brand-use content includes organic usage for your owned social channels.
    Paid usage, raw footage, rush delivery, whitelisting, in-store use, or
    perpetual rights can be added by quote.
  </p>
</section>
